# Chris Hempel

## User Services

Phone: **512-475-9479** |
Email: **[hempel@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:hempel@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Chris joined TACC in 1997 as the Director of User Services. He evaluates available technology, plans for future technology, and implements technology upgrades. Chris coordinates training and integration across different groups and he also deals with vendor relations and budgeting. Prior to joining TACC, Chris worked for Cray Research as an Applications Analyst.

### Education

**B.A., Mathematics**  

The University of Texas at Austin